    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition and has been kept in a climate-controlled environment by its original owner. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining a factory-level deep shine with no stone chips or scratches, while the interior still carries that new-car scent and shows zero signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, with a full service history and every component functioning exactly as it did the day it left the dealership. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly preserved example of this model.",
      "price": 48500.0,
